msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/ma/extras.py:docstring
#: of numpy.ma.extras.stack:24
msgid ""
"If provided, the destination array will have this dtype. Cannot be provided "
"together with `out`."
